    • configure

      @Deprecated public static void configure()
      Deprecated.
      Use Micrometer's default NamingConvention.
      Configures all the MeterRegistrys added to the Metrics.globalRegistry to use the NamingConventions provided by this class. DropwizardMeterRegistry and PrometheusMeterRegistry will be configured to use dropwizard() and prometheus() respectively. This method is a shortcut for: 
      
 configure(Metrics.globalRegistry);

    • configure

      @Deprecated public static void configure​(MeterRegistry registry)
      Deprecated.
      Use Micrometer's default NamingConvention.
      Configures the specified MeterRegistry to use the NamingConventions provided by this class. DropwizardMeterRegistry and PrometheusMeterRegistry will be configured to use dropwizard() and prometheus() respectively. A CompositeMeterRegistry will be configured recursively.
